  "cooked": "<p>It seems there\u2019s ongoing work on CoinSwap.</p>\n<p>Summary of the protocol:\n</p><aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://opensats.org/blog/developing-advancements-in-onchain-privacy\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/3/39baa96481bbdaa8ed711293b3da66445eaef359.png\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"FF6B01\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://opensats.org/blog/developing-advancements-in-onchain-privacy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" title=\"12:00AM - 28 February 2025\">OpenSats \u2013 28 Feb 25</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:690/345;\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7729743538d90b1a714c5bf759de4af4b19b89fe_2_690x345.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"796644\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://opensats.org/blog/developing-advancements-in-onchain-privacy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Advancements in On-Chain Privacy</a></h3>\n\n  <p>An impact report from the front-lines of bitcoin development.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://opensats.org/topics/coinswap\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/3/39baa96481bbdaa8ed711293b3da66445eaef359.png\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"FF6B01\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://opensats.org/topics/coinswap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">OpenSats</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:690/362;\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7de97655bd94e5ddd858fb055f495d8da0a58ee1_2_690x362.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"F0F0EF\" width=\"690\" height=\"362\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://opensats.org/topics/coinswap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Coinswap - OpenSats Topics</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Atomic multi-hop swaps that move coins through intermediate keys so the spender of an input cannot be linked to the receiver of the final output.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>An actively developed implementation:\n</p><aside class=\"onebox githubrepo\" data-onebox-src=\"https://github.com/citadel-tech/coinswap\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/citadel-tech/coinswap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">github.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"github-row\" data-github-private-repo=\"false\">\n  <img width=\"690\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f54d627e02dae26bac746becf7f462acf719f3e8_2_690x344.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" data-dominant-color=\"F3F2F2\">\n\n  <h3><a href=\"https://github.com/citadel-tech/coinswap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">GitHub - citadel-tech/coinswap: Functioning, minimal-viable binaries and libraries...</a></h3>\n\n    <p><span class=\"github-repo-description\">Functioning, minimal-viable binaries and libraries to perform a trustless, p2p Maxwell-Belcher Coinswap Protocol</span></p>\n</div>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://github.com/citadel-tech/coinswap/milestone/1\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/b/bad3e5f9ad67c1ddf145107ce7032ac1d7b22563.svg\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/citadel-tech/coinswap/milestone/1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">GitHub</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:690/344;\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f54d627e02dae26bac746becf7f462acf719f3e8_2_690x345.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"F3F2F2\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://github.com/citadel-tech/coinswap/milestone/1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">citadel-tech/coinswap</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Functioning, minimal-viable binaries and libraries to perform a trustless, p2p Maxwell-Belcher Coinswap Protocol - citadel-tech/coinswap</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>Protocol spec:\n</p><aside class=\"onebox githubrepo\" data-onebox-src=\"https://github.com/citadel-tech/Coinswap-Protocol-Specification\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/citadel-tech/Coinswap-Protocol-Specification\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">github.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"github-row\" data-github-private-repo=\"false\">\n  <img width=\"690\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/78b49a08ee12b6b491aca558b600c942738598b2_2_690x344.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" data-dominant-color=\"F4F4F5\">\n\n  <h3><a href=\"https://github.com/citadel-tech/Coinswap-Protocol-Specification\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">GitHub - citadel-tech/Coinswap-Protocol-Specification: Detailed protocol and other technical...</a></h3>\n\n    <p><span class=\"github-repo-description\">Detailed protocol and other technical dcumentations of Coinswap.</span></p>\n</div>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=321228.0\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=321228.0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">bitcointalk.org</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    \n\n<h3><a href=\"https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=321228.0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CoinSwap:  Transaction graph disjoint trustless trading</a></h3>\n\n  <p>CoinSwap:  Transaction graph disjoint trustless trading</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>An older PoC from Chris Belcher:\n</p><aside class=\"onebox githubrepo\" data-onebox-src=\"https://github.com/bitcoin-teleport/teleport-transactions\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcoin-teleport/teleport-transactions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">github.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"github-row\" data-github-private-repo=\"false\">\n  <img width=\"690\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7ae5f38fbc7c437240cbda45ba1fb2c8c77dac9b_2_690x344.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" data-dominant-color=\"F5F2F3\">\n\n  <h3><a href=\"https://github.com/bitcoin-teleport/teleport-transactions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">GitHub - bitcoin-teleport/teleport-transactions: CoinSwap implementation</a></h3>\n\n    <p><span class=\"github-repo-description\">CoinSwap implementation</span></p>\n</div>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
